SUMMARY:Urban Tree Planting Community Meeting (Charlotte)
DESCRIPTION:You are invited to join us for a community meeting at Ivory Baker Recreation Center to share your input and learn about volunteering to help plant trees in your neighborhood this spring. Light refreshments will be provided. \nTree planting sites are 1712 West Trade Street and the intersection of Frazier Avenue & West Fifth Street in Charlotte\, NC! \nREGISTER HERE
URL:https://ncwf.org/event/urban-tree-planting-community-meeting-charlotte/
CATEGORIES:Featured
ATTACH;FMTTYPE=image/jpeg:https://ncwf.org/wp-content/uploads/communitymeet-1.jpg
